<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>FinalProject</title>
  <!-- Standard Meta -->
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">

  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application' %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

  <!--fonts-->
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway:100,400,200,300' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nothing+You+Could+Do' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

  <!--gmaps4rails-->
  <script src="http://maps.google.com/maps/api/js?v=3.13&sensor=false&libraries=geometrykey=AIzaSyDZPtO2jQcyMxVWc4pgtazVivWuM2qiDiU" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src='http://google-maps-utility-library-v3.googlecode.com/svn/tags/markerclustererplus/2.0.14/src/markerclusterer_packed.js' type='text/javascript'></script>

</head>
<body>
<%= image_tag "homepage.jpg" %>
  <div class="ui page grid">
    <div class="column">
      <div class="ui text menu">
        <% if user_signed_in? %>
          <i class="item">
            <a href="#about">About</a>
          </i>
          <i class="item">
            <%= link_to "Scores", games_path %>
          </i>
          <i class="item">
            <%= link_to "Update Account", edit_user_registration_path %>
          </i>
          <i class="item">
            <%= link_to "Log Out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete %>
          </i>
          <i class="item">
            <%= link_to "Play!", new_game_path %>
          </i>
        <% else %>
          <i class="item">
            <a href="#about">About</a>
          </i>
          <i class="item">
            <%= link_to "Log In", new_user_session_path %>
          </i>
          <i class="item">
            <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path %>
          </i>
          <i class="item">
            <%= link_to "Play!", new_game_path %>
          </i>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="header"><%= link_to "Wayfarer", root_path %></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ui vertical rectangle test ad"></div>

  <div class="ui inverted vertical segment">
    <div class="ui very relaxed stackable page grid">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="column">
          <h1 class="center aligned ui inverted header">
            <a name="about">
              How to Play
            </a>
          </h1>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="eight wide column">
          <div class="ui inverted animated selection list">
            <div class="item" style="text-align:center">
              GAME PLAY
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>Create an account by clicking on "Sign Up" in the menu above.
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>Click "Play" to be transported to a Google Street View somewhere in the world...
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>You have 30 seconds to walk around in Google Street View to figure out where you are. **HINT be on the lookout for street signs in other languages, names of stores, or famous landmarks!
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>If you know where you are, click on the "Guess" button at the bottom of the screen. Otherwise, once the 30 seconds are up, a map will pop up on the screen.
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>Zoom in on the map and drag the pin to the location you think you have been placed in. Take your time here, the timer has stopped!
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>Once you've placed you're pin, click "Submit" to submit your answer.
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>You will be redirected to a map with two pins in it. One pin is the location you guessed, and the other is the location you were placed in. See how close you got!
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>Click on "Play Next Level" to play again!
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="eight wide column">
          <div class="ui inverted animated selection list">
            <div class="item" style="text-align:center">
              SCORING
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>Your score is determined by how many miles away your guess was from your destination. You want to get the LOWEST score, as in closest to your destination!
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>You can click on "Scores" in the menu to see all of your scores.
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <i class="angle double right icon"></i>There is also a leaderboard here with the top scores in the world on the levels you have played.
            </div>
            <button class="ui teal animated button huge button">
              <div class="visible content">Let's Play!</div>
              <div class="hidden content"><%= link_to "Let's Play!", new_game_path %></div>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<div class="ui footer segment">
  <%= image_tag "codecore.jpg" %>
</div>

</body>
</html>
